Definition: Auguste Comte's positivistic philosophy that metaphysics and theology should be replaced by a hierarchy of sciences from mathematics at the base to sociology at the top
Synonyms: positivism, Auguste, Comte, s, positivistic, philosophy, that, metaphysics, and, theology, should, be, replaced, by, a, hierarchy, of, sciences, from, mathematics, at, the, base, to, sociology, top
Category: noun.cognition
